<DT><A HREF="http://pouet.net/prod.php?which=56410">No PETs allowed!</A></DT> 
<DD>A really cool demo for a 50Hz 4032 PET (with CRTC).
There also now is a version without frequency check, that you can try on a 60Hz PET:
<a href="http://orb-demo.net/files/no_pets_allowed_nohz_check.zip">no_pets_allowed_nohz_check.zip</a>.
</DD>
</DL>
